- `v2 : Vector α n` represented as `⟨⟨hd2, tl2⟩, n⟩` where `hd2` is the head and `tl2` is the tail of the list representing `v2`
- `h : ∀ (i : Fin n), v1[i] = v2[i]` which is `∀ (i : Fin n), (hd1 :: tl1)[i] = (hd2 :: tl2)[i]`
